- 4 new integration tests (`analytics-timeseries.spec.ts`) — all green (per-file shared-DB).
- Playwright @ `:9000` (jaalyantra.com): Hourly (24h axis, noon spike) + Daily (30-day axis, Jun 18-21 peak) both render real data, toggle works, no new console errors. Typecheck of changed admin files clean.

